      },
      "date": "2013-03-05 21:35:59.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, approved\n\nI'm OK to disable this test for b2_1 to get the test results passing.  However, I'd also like you to submit another patch for master that takes test_14b out of the ALWAYS_EXCEPT list.  I think that with the changes made in this patch to the test itself that it should be working properly.\n\nThe patch should have a Test-Parameters testlist that runs replay-dual several times to ensure this test is working consistently.",
